Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.19,0:00:18.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:20.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近還真多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:37.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:40.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我是常盤台的婚後光子還如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:50.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:56.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天好像也發生了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:56.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:00:59.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的宿舍怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:02.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心  我們那好像沒什麼震動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:06.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明同樣在第7學區還真讓人匪夷所思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:09.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大圄老師  那麼這…今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:12.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:13.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:18.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第二學期轉進來的轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:22.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  從現在起就是你的室友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:24.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然這樣安排真的不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:27.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為我校的風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:27.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(370,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:29.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多幫助她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:33.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:38.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫春上衿衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:14.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從第19學區來的轉學生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在這個時候不覺得很少見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:21.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常來說都應該是挑在新學期才對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:23.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:27.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:31.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是初春的室友也就是我的候補摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:37.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:39.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是春上衿衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:45.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盤台中學的白井黑子和她的學姐御阪美琴學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:49.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是和我們同班的佐天淚子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:04:00.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…那個…正當我去車站接春上同學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:03.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家公司就來通知了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:07.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來搬家公司也應該稍微考慮一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:09.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  要做點什麼才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:11.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看見空間移動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(370,328)\fs18}Teleport
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:29.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了  我這個程度的空間移動能力者在學園都市裏可沒幾個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:29.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,328)\fs18}Teleporter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:32.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  盡快收拾完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:49.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:51.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:55.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  既然收拾得比預想中還要快不如去哪玩一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:56.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:58.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是贊成的時候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春和我接下來要參加協同會議
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:04.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協同會議是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於風紀委員與警備員的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:12.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像關於最近頻發的地震的話題什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於地震的會議？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:19.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  御阪學姐跟我三個人一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了再匯合不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:30.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說佐天同學御阪學姐是很善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這結束以後馬上就會到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:34.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:36.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:40.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別掀春上同學的裙子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要做這種事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那個…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  去哪好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:53.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學有想去的地方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:57.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還…不怎麼熟悉這個學區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:05:59.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:01.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…當然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到最能增進友誼的地方  就是這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:11.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來跟佐天同學你們第一次相遇的時候也來過這裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:13.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:18.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}你的嘴邊粘了很多奶油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:19.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來黑子她們還真夠辛苦的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:24.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會為了場地震風紀委員要跟警備員進行協同會議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:24.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:24.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼事件還說得過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:29.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我雖然閉口不說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:32.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實關於這個有一個非常熱門的傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}警備員第7學區本部  第一會議室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:36.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於最近頻繁發生的地震原因已經查明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得出的結論是這並不是地震
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:41.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確的來說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:44.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂雜開放？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:44.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! 亂雜開放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個吧  傢俱什麼的不知為什麼晃來晃去鬧鬼現象…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震時該有的縱波和橫波都沒有檢測到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:55.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是超自然現象啊  超自然現象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:07:01.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會有學生發生恐慌  在此再次重申
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:03.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是什麼超自然現象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:09.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂雜開放的原因是RSPK綜合癥的同時多處發生所引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:09.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(120,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,146)\fs15\bord0\fad(250,0)}RSPK綜合癥所指的是，能力者暫時性地失去自我約束力，\N在無自覺的情況下使自己的能力進入的失控狀態以其現象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,232)\fs15\bord0\fad(250,0)}雖然各種能力者所引發的現象五花八門，但當這個現象在同時發生的時候，\N失控的能力會互相融合，就會一律以亂雜開放現象表現出來。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,313)\fs15\bord0\fad(250,0)}而且，這種亂雜開放現象其規模擴大的時候，\N會給人一種如地震之類的自然現象的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:11.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RSPK綜合癥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時多處發生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:18.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之後的話題有請先進狀況救助隊的特蕾斯蒂娜來說明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:26.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我是剛才被介紹的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:29.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先進狀況救助隊的特蕾斯蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:32.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂RSPK綜合癥是指
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:35.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力者暫時性地失去自我約束力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:39.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有自覺的情況下使自己的能力失控
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:41.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然個人引發的現象五花八門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是當這些在同時發生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:46.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失控的能力會互相融合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:51.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會一律以亂雜開放的現象表現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:51.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:56.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這種亂雜開放現象規模擴大的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:56.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:08:00.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會給人一種  如地震之類的自然現象的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是這次地震的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:10.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然關於RSPK綜合癥在同時多處發生的原因現在還在調查中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:15.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在部分學生之間愚蠢地將這種現象當成是靈異現象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:17.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是來自異次元的波動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊的等離子體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:23.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如  是統合理事會秘密進行的地下實驗什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:24.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:29.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在著引發群體失控而擴大受害程度的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:33.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次之所以召集各位風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:33.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:37.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是防止學生因為興趣而將這個傳聞四處傳播
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而加緊注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:43.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說很快就會有一個大現象出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:46.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:51.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  春上同學的第19學區
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亂雜開放的多發區吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:54.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:59.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著  覺得這種事情很有趣就這樣聲張可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的發生了可不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:08.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比預想中的結束得要快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:11.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警備員在這之後還有會議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:11.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:14.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固法學姐發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:19.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RSPK綜合癥的同時多處發生根本沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  這次的對應方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺讓人有點懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:28.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不就得依靠這方面專業的人們進行調查了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:32.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們亂猜也沒什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣說也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:36.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學  你們現在在哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:44.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學  接下來要玩什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:47.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春真是的  都得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人也真夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:52.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在哪見過的硬幣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:01.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打地鼠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:05.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人懷念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:08.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…第一次來這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個個鑽出來好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:14.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:17.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個…別光看著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:20.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:27.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人獲得樂趣的方式都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:32.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:34.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:35.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四次有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:36.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家去拍那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:42.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:51.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發送
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:56.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不可思議的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:04.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很可愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:09.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼的  讓我想起來以前的初春
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:10.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:14.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  剛入學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:25.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花大會的海報？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來這不就是今天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  大家去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯呢  穿著浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:38.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:48.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次穿浴衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:50.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會太長了點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:58.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:01.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是像這樣用帶子調整下擺長度的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很難的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:06.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:06.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:12.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…先把前面合在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:16.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的項鏈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:20.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就好像是我的護身符一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:23.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身符麼  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  趕快把浴衣穿好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:30.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…把前面合起來之後是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:36.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把浴衣的領邊向上提20公分…是這樣麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:38.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你那麼照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同學真是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:48.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我姑且也算是個風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:48.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:54.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  最近幹的全是打掃城市衛生和尋找失物這樣的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:13:00.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  只要是力所能及的事情我都會做好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:02.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放心地交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:08.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然把我叫過來  我還以為是什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:11.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐…佐天同學…快救救我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:15.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:22.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  佐天同學  一下子就穿得那麼漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:25.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  不快點的話就來不及了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:30.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此  一開始就拜託佐天同學就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  初春你也很努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:38.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就輪到我來出力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:43.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時不是總也通不過風紀委員的考試嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:43.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:48.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這樣  我做別的事也變得缺乏自信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:53.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的初春  總是讓人放心不下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:14:00.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對那樣一個我  佐天同學不總是給我鼓勵為我分憂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:03.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:08.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為那樣  我才能通過考試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:16.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在我才會希望這次能夠為春上同學做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:22.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…雖然只有我一個人的話有些靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:26.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的事  我很高興初春同學能夠成為我的室友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請你多多照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:30.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:34.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不知不覺就變得那麼出色了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  明明是我生日比較早的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意細節
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:41.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼嘛  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:44.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  別亂動  不然就穿不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:53.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:54.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:08.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回沒問題了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:16.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有我們宿舍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連煙花大會的日子門限都不變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:23.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  那樣亂動的話衣服會散掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:24.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:29.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了  好不容易穿一回浴衣  居然又在底下穿了短褲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:31.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛  反正也看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:35.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注重一些看不見的細節才是少女的美德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:38.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  今天固法學姐不來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:42.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是要調查一些關於亂雜開放的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:42.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:46.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎自從會議結束後就在在意著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  確實很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:53.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RSPK綜合癥居然會同時暴發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒完沒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:01.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網上的情報也只有這個程度麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:05.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:08.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學也好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:15.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:18.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有夜市啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  還開了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:23.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:24.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  像那樣跑的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:27.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學  我們也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:01.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:04.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛  反正現在是祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迎合節日的氣氛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:07.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒轍…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:11.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那些車是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MAR
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:15.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是先進狀況救助隊的車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:18.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了最近的亂雜開放事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:18.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:21.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂雜開放？ 那麼說來那個傳聞是真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:21.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(187,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:26.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一在這種人山人海的地方爆發亂雜開放的話可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:26.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:30.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  居然要在那樣的警戒下觀賞煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:33.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大煞風景
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  我知道一個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:44.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏  是個秘密地點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  又竄上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺肚子裏也會咚咚迴響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:57.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  咚咚迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:11.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是也去了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:16.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些在意  可就算再繼續調查也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AIM擴散力場…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉屋——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍵屋——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}玉屋和鍵屋是江戶時代兩位有名的煙火師的煙火店的屋號  後演變為觀賞煙火時的口號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:31.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:34.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉屋——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:38.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:44.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:53.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我以前也曾有像初春同學和佐天同學那樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:18:59.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:03.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:05.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:09.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們這是上哪兒去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:14.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在特意為我們營造二人空間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:17.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  我們也像煙火那樣激情綻放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:19.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱…熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚也真美妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  你的手機在響
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:25.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時候有什麼事嗎  固法學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:32.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快聽我說  是關於亂雜開放的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:32.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(375,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:36.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查找資料固然重要  不過你也稍微休息一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:38.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火可漂亮了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:44.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RSPK綜合癥同時暴發的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:48.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是針對AIM擴散力場的人為干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:51.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,針對AIM擴散力場的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:55.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  這一連串的亂雜開放事件的發生並非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:55.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(325,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:58.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏…到底在哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:06.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是有人在刻意引發事件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:12.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:13.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  白井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:14.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:17.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是  亂雜開放？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:17.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(335,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:26.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:28.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:32.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:48.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學  不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是千鈞一髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:05.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:07.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:09.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:16.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:17.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:22.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學  你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:23.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:25.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:33.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏好像崩塌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事故了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:32.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏…到底在哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.69,0:23:34.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在右邊  春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:36.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走過頭了  再往左邊點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:38.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在砍西瓜麼

